{"word":"παραίτησις","slug":"παραίτησις","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>παραίτησις</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>from <a href='S:παραιτέομαι'><el>παραιτέομαι</el></a>\n<el>(παραίτησις, εως,) </el><p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>earnest prayer</i>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>a deprecating</i>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>III. </b><i>an interceding for, begging off</i>, <b><a href='S:Demosthenes'>Dem.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}